{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/Sorc_pre_release.gif?t=1738064790\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tactical Roguelike Deckbuilder with ability-based combat, fueled by card synergies. Build a powerful deck to support your hero. Use abilities to wipe out hordes of enemies. Discover powerful combos within the near-endless variety of composite cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/Amazon_pre_release.gif?t=1738064790\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <strong>Features:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Abilities supported by cards</strong>: Hero has 3 abilities that cost mana. Cards generate mana, buff abilities, and heal hero.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Area effect based combat</strong>: Abilities with large range don't hit very hard. Abilities with high damage don't reach very far. Sequence them cleverly! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Experimentation without punishment</strong>: You can <strong>Undo</strong> anything played that turn. Try different approaches with no penalty. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Composite cards</strong>: Combination of interchangeable statuses and cycles produces near-endless variety of cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132780/extras/Cards_pre_release.gif?t=1738064790\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <strong>Forestygian currently has:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>7</strong> heroes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>54</stron